    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>"New fathers" indoor cap, usually decorated and plumed. Traditionally worn in the Netherlands for nine to ten days after the birth of a child. No equivalent in English language or culture.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
